node.text: Drop your favorite line below 😂 until next time, Tuesday with Ted!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dede Raad on August 12, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and child.

node.text: & she’s off 😭 happy first ever day of school baby girl! She cried. I cried. & now I’m sitting here counting down the minutes until we can go pick her up. What a freaking feeling y’all 🍎 #firstday #school

node.text: We blinked & now have a kid in school..will I ever be ready?! Met Rosie girl’s sweet teachers tonight. We have a couple more days until she officially starts Mother’s Day Out but praying that this transition is smooth 😭Wow am I so 👏🏽 grateful 👏🏽 for the educators of this world. How did your kids transition to school?? I’m more worried about me than her 🙈 dress is @pinklily & the third time I’ve worn in in a week! Linked in bio 🤍

node.text: Year 9: year of pottery & willow 🙌🏽 love you husband & your sweet soul. Here’s to many more years & many more babies 😍 Also love YOU, if had faith in my pottery skills & voted for me but I had the sad guy (on the left) hahahaa #anniversary #datenight

Cheers to another good week! My white tshirt is only $30 jeans are on sale from @express #expresspartner #expressedition #sunday #sundaystyle #houston #weekend #momlife

node.text: My babies + the weekend = so happy 😃 these 2 came at the most perfect time for our life when I personally needed them the most. Im trying to soak it up & enjoy the moments but I’m already worried it’s going by too fast 😭 Like how do we have a 3 month old (the most smiliest baby) and sis is starting MDO so soon 😭. Mama heart can’t take it! My romper was swooooon for yesterday’s activities. Comfy & flattering plus 25 off today only with code dede25 from @vicidolls #twinning #weekend #mybabies #sundaystyle

node.text: Anyone realize how unfair it is that Monday is so far from Friday but Friday is so close to Monday?? Guess we just have to make those Friday’s count👏🏼 planned a date night out for some one on one time with the Ted and had to pick up a couple pieces from Tarjayy. Don’t worry hubs, didn’t do too much damage and found my new fav jeans for under $30, thought you’d be proud 🤪 now let’s try some cocktails 🎉 @target @TargetStyle #targetpartner #targetstyle

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Dede Raad on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 3 people and outdoors.

node.text: Happy house warming party sis 🎉 Hot girl summer edition haha🤣☀️ Finally beat Katy at her own game and threw her a surprise house warming party on a random Thursday. She’s been pulling shenanigans like these on me since we were kids so felt like it was time to pull a fast one on her. I’ve seen this pink limo from Sam's everywhere on tiktok and thought it was perfect to help me pull this off 🤣 @samsclub #samsclubpartner #samsclubsummer
